l reach of flood impacts on population\nlifestyles. The analysis and findings also provide novel data-driven insights\nfor public official and emergency managers to examine, measure, and monitor a\ncritical milestone in community recovery trajectory based on the return of\nlifestyles to normalcy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2022 21:35:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 13:01:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
