y consistent with $\\Lambda$CDM cosmology. Our\nmethods can be readily scaled to analyse upcoming large galaxy surveys and\nachieve accurate tests of the cosmological model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2022 06:39:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2022 03:41:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
