 current autoregressive model on input sequences of\n3 seconds, and obtains superior audio quality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2022 10:10:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 09:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-14"}
